name: the-pessimist-susanr-60240
description:
One of one as a special edition in The Pessimist series. Generated by a hand-coded python application, the Pessimist series is built on an instruction set that combines rectangles, ellipses, clipping paths, and fills to create geometric, conceptual, modern works that are structured in their composition, but organic in their rendition. All quantities, sizes, positions, and pallets are generated by the application. susanr-26359 was rendered with a special friend and fellow art lover. The art exists as an svg to preserve the integrity of the original and allow viewing and reproduction at any size.

Generative art created by MaxBore.
